div.div: Rettou Hito no Maken Tsukai Sukiruboudo o Kushi Shite Saikyou ni Itaru

Tohru Minasuki, a normal office worker, is reborn in another world after falling through a dimensional rift. A god grants him an ability called Skill Board upon his reincarnation. Taking advantage of this, he acquires essential skills—and an overpowered skill called Magic Blade. Despite his status as a stray—those known as inferiors for being seemingly incapable of leveling up—he pressed forward on the path to becoming the strongest!
(Source: K-Manga)
Adventure, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

Aldred, the leader of a kingdom’s A-ranked party, "Black Silver," has accomplished the task of slaying a dragon. However, he who has pursued strength his whole life has lost sight of his goal from taking down a monster of the strongest species. As he worried about what to do next in his life, it was the scenery of Nordende that popped up in his mind; A rural village by the countryside, full of natural beauty, which he only visited once during a quest in the past.
After declaring the disbandment of his party, he heads towards Nordende for a comfortable, relaxing life.
